  <brief_title>ACL Reconstruction With the TLS Technique</brief_title>
  <official_title>ACL Reconstruction With the TLS Technique (Tape Locking Screw) and Return to Sport: Serial 5-year Independent Designers</official_title>
  <sponsors>
